                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
                                        <h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
                                            In Conversation                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            ‘Humour is a thread we hang onto. It punctures through the fog of guilt.’<br><br>

Momtaza Mehri in conversation with Warsan Shire.                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                                        <a href="https://granta.com/in-conversation-mary-jean-chan-andrew-mcmillan/">
